hopobject.body: Children with disabilities super pharmacy locations Enter the world of hire cars and you enter a world not dissimilar to budget airlines where the price you pay covers the service in its most basic form and anything else incurs a further, frequently hefty, charge. The difference is that when you hire a car, the thing you're paying extra for probably has an acronym. It's a world of CDW (Collision Damage Waiver), SCDW (Super Collision Damage Waiver), LDW (Loss Damage Waiver), PEP (Personal Effects Protection), TP (Theft Protection), STP (Super Theft Protection) and more.
